				<td colspan="2"><span>Spell Awareness is right up there with Target's Target for group Leader AAs, IMHO.  Let's you know which mobs to Bellow/Mez interrupt (heal spells) and which to just ignore or toss up a Veeshan to resist.  Or use Dark Echo if you actually have it (/e mumbles something about POS rare spells).
<br />

<br />
But for raids it is next to useless.  If you do your homework you already know what they are going to cast.  And if you didn't do your homework...  *drumroll* Spell Awareness doesn't tell you what boss mobs cast.  Absolute lameness.  You have to resist the spell once to get it's name, same as if you didn't have Spell Awareness.  What a joke.</span></td>
