				<td colspan="2"><span>Very useful AA...
<br />

<br />
Easy to see when a mob is gating... CH'ing... dispelling and so forth. Also its great cause you can always see if a heal is inbound for the tank etc. I played my necro together with another necro in an LDoN, and thanks to Spell Awarness we didnt cast the same drains/debuffs that dont stack with eachother hehe.
<br />

<br />
Also a good way to uncover wether or not someone in the group are just exp-leeching... harr harr... caught a few of those too with Spell Awarness...
